node.text: During my creek mission in Tennessee I stumbled upon this curious smallmouth bass that decided he’d like some air time.  #fish #fishing #bass #summer #animals

node.title: Wild Creek Fish Inspects the Camera

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jonathan Barzacchini in St. Clair Shores, Michigan. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Getting tossed by mega waves, and drifting through Uber schools of perch.. it’s what St. Clair is all about. Very tough but fun couple of days on this big bodacious lake. One of my favorite things ever is learning a new fishery and chasing smallmouth in the process.

node.text: It has been a smallmouth filled week up here in Maine. @grant_langmore7 and I  have chased down stripers, fished 7 different lakes and competed in the second Maine derb of the season all in a matter of a few days. I know I’ve been lacking on the uploads but just know the best is coming. Thank you wieners for being patient 🙏🏻

node.text: Had such a freakin fun day with @rygid34 fishing my first team derb up here in Maine. Met so many genuine, welcoming anglers today on the water. Weather was perfect, bite was on fire.. the times up here just too good.
